definition: tree trunk/main part of sth/to manage/to work/to do/capable/cadre/to kill (slang)/to fuck (vulgar)

sentences.english: When she was building her first foundling asylum, what was he doing?
sentences.chinese: 她造第一间育婴堂的时候，他干吗去了？

sentences.english: Why don't you take your padded coat off?
sentences.chinese: 你干吗不把棉大衣脱掉？

sentences.english: Why not look in the local paper?
sentences.chinese: 干吗不去查一下当地的报纸？
年轻姑娘把那两个字念道了两遍，“自由干吗？”

sentences.english: Say, why don't you get married with all this money to burn?
sentences.chinese: 嗨，你的钱多得都烧包了，干吗不讨个老婆？

sentences.english: Why buy books when you can use the library?
A:What did you do over Spring Break?
I know they'll go higher, but why be greedy.
sentences.chinese: 我知道价格还会创新高，又干吗要这么贪婪呢？

sentences.english: Why is you brother staggering about the room like that?
sentences.chinese: 你弟弟干吗那样在房间里晃来晃去？

sentences.english: Besides, I want you to tell me why I should not go in for philanthropy.
sentences.chinese: 此外，请你告诉我干吗我不应沉迷于博爱主义。

sentences.english: Gossip girl: I bet you’re wondering what gossip girl is doing up so early.
sentences.chinese: 我敢肯定你们都在疑惑绯闻少女大清早的在干吗。

sentences.english: I am a union president, a day so many things to do, why do this?
sentences.chinese: 我是个工会主席，每天那么多事情要做，干吗做这个？

sentences.english: Oh, if that's case, what should we stand here waiting for?
sentences.chinese: 嗬，既然这样，我们干吗站在这里？

sentences.english: Catherine, why are you crying, love?
sentences.chinese: 凯瑟琳，你干吗哭呀，宝贝儿？

sentences.english: WILLY:Why do you get American when I like Swiss?
sentences.chinese: 威利你明知道我爱吃瑞士奶酪，干吗买美国的？

what are you doing?/what's he up to?
